3. cs.PH (Physics) is relevant as the paper deals with the physical properties of the optical channel. 
4. cs.OC (Optimization and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the optimization of codes and receivers to achieve higher communication rates. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with communication channels and information transmission.
